title: Angel and Faith 24 (2013) (Tablet Edition)
description:
I adjusted the resolution and compression of the original scan for easier reading on tablets and to save space. All credit goes to the original scanner for their hard work. I have added 'Tablet Edition' to the name to avoid confusion.

Enjoy and please seed back.


Angel and Faith 24

By:     	Christos Gage, Rebekah Isaacs, Dan Jackson, Steve Morris	
Type:   	Comics
Genres:   	Action-Adventure, Horror
Series:   	Angel
Publisher:   	Dark Horse	
Pub. Date:  	July 31, 2013
Format:         CBZ

Angel and Faith will need all the help they can get when it comes to stopping this season's ubervillains from unleashing a magic-fueled plague on the earth. Enter an archmage, a former Watcher, and two socialites who've dabbled in magic . . . Will it be enough?

* Final Arc!

* Battle to the death!
